<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:08:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>总理办公室指责以色列医院侵犯获救人质的隐私</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/prime-ministers-office-accuses-israeli-hospital-of-violating-rescued-hostages-privacy/00000190-5605-dc65-abff-7e2f14800000</link><description>总理办公室在一次没有医院代表出席的会议上表示，“医院工作人员不断给人质拍照，他们的照片未经同意就被分享，医疗队披露了有关他们被囚禁和健康状况的详细信息”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 09:38:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/prime-ministers-office-accuses-israeli-hospital-of-violating-rescued-hostages-privacy/00000190-5605-dc65-abff-7e2f14800000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列陆军预备役军人解释为什么他们拒绝继续在加沙服役</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/three-israeli-army-reservists-explain-why-they-refuse-to-continue-serving-in-gaza/00000190-5014-d3c0-a5d4-737644c90000</link><description>尤瓦尔被要求烧毁两栋住宅楼；迈克尔意识到在他观察到的每次爆炸中可能有多少平民丧生；当以色列进入拉法时，塔尔崩溃了。他们愿意为拒绝在加沙服役而付出代价</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 07:45:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/three-israeli-army-reservists-explain-why-they-refuse-to-continue-serving-in-gaza/00000190-5014-d3c0-a5d4-737644c90000</guid></item><item><title>面对每天的停电和昂贵的面包，埃及人对加沙的困境不再那么感兴趣</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/facing-daily-power-outages-and-costly-bread-egyptians-are-less-interested-in-gazas-woes/00000190-5747-de5e-abd0-ff770f3d0000</link><description>埃及总理对天然气故障和“邻国”的言论引发了人们对开罗能源短缺及其与以色列关系的猜测。尽管遭到否认，但自以色列入侵拉法以来，开罗的愤怒仍在加剧</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 03:01:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/facing-daily-power-outages-and-costly-bread-egyptians-are-less-interested-in-gazas-woes/00000190-5747-de5e-abd0-ff770f3d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列开始全国集会，要求人质协议、立即选举</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israelis-plan-countrywide-rallies-calling-for-hostage-deal-immediate-election/00000190-5762-def3-a5b6-df6749220000</link><description>抗议者封锁了以色列中部的主要高速公路；计划在凯撒利亚和耶路撒冷总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的官邸举行大型晚间示威</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 03:00:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israelis-plan-countrywide-rallies-calling-for-hostage-deal-immediate-election/00000190-5762-def3-a5b6-df6749220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙城发动“大规模”罢工；以色列国防军军官在约旦河西岸袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-live/gallant-israel-could-return-lebanon-to-stone-age-but-does-not-want-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-5780-d63a-a7b2-5f9f7c070000</link><description>16 名以色列国防军士兵在杰宁袭击中受伤 ■ 英国安全公司表示，据报道船只在也门附近被“击中” ■ 利库德集团部长表示，以色列必须“控制加沙地带”，将其与埃及切断联系 ■ 报告：以色列在叙利亚造成 3 人死亡、11 人受伤归因于袭击 ■ 勇敢：以色列可以摧毁黎巴嫩，但不希望与真主党发生战争</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:31:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-live/gallant-israel-could-return-lebanon-to-stone-age-but-does-not-want-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-5780-d63a-a7b2-5f9f7c070000</guid></item><item><title>总理的律师告诉法庭，内塔尼亚胡只能在 2025 年 3 月的腐败审判中作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/pms-lawyers-tell-court-netanyahu-can-only-testify-in-corruption-trial-in-march-2025/00000190-5605-def3-a5b6-de2755a00000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的律师表示，他们需要九个月的时间才能提出辩方的陈述。耶路撒冷地方法院的审判因调查内容、新冠肺炎以及因战争而关闭法院的争论而多次停止</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:18:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/pms-lawyers-tell-court-netanyahu-can-only-testify-in-corruption-trial-in-march-2025/00000190-5605-def3-a5b6-de2755a00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡助手担心利库德集团最高议员将破坏正统派豁免法案草案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-aides-fear-top-likud-lawmaker-will-sabotage-haredi-draft-exemption-bill/00000190-557c-dc65-abff-7d7f83860000</link><description>讨论该法案的委员会主席、利库德集团议员尤利·埃德尔斯坦(Yuli Edelstein)表示，“如果该法案不能以广泛共识获得通过，它就根本不会通过。”在反对派议员的反对下，埃德尔斯坦还推迟了议会关于延长以色列国防军预备役服役的投票</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:01:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-aides-fear-top-likud-lawmaker-will-sabotage-haredi-draft-exemption-bill/00000190-557c-dc65-abff-7d7f83860000</guid></item><item><title>美国高级官员：与以色列合作解决武器延误问题，重型炸弹转移仍停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-working-with-israel-to-resolve-arms-delay-heavy-bomb-transfer-still-halted/00000190-55b2-dc65-abff-7dbbff410000</link><description>华盛顿的国防部长约夫·加兰特描述了武器“瓶颈”方面的“重大进展”。他还批评内塔尼亚胡公开哀叹总理所谓的“故意”延迟武器运输</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 19:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-working-with-israel-to-resolve-arms-delay-heavy-bomb-transfer-still-halted/00000190-55b2-dc65-abff-7dbbff410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会提出法案，永久禁止半岛电视台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-parliament-advances-bill-to-make-law-banning-al-jazeera-permanent/00000190-54c0-dac0-a798-77d789710000</link><description>该法案永久立法目前是一项暂停外国媒体广播的临时命令，如果被认为损害国家安全，将返回政府委员会进一步审议</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 18:48:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-parliament-advances-bill-to-make-law-banning-al-jazeera-permanent/00000190-54c0-dac0-a798-77d789710000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡最后一次国会演讲猛烈抨击民主党。这个有不同的目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-26/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-last-congress-speech-slammed-democrats-this-one-has-a-different-target/00000190-556a-de50-af9b-7fee35df0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡最近在2011年和2015年的国会演讲的目标是削弱巴拉克·奥巴马总统及其民主党。这次剧本反转了</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 18:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-26/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-last-congress-speech-slammed-democrats-this-one-has-a-different-target/00000190-556a-de50-af9b-7fee35df0000</guid></item><item><title>鲍曼惨败后，美国进步人士能否在不疏远选民的情况下应对亲以色列机器？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/can-progressives-tackle-the-pro-israel-machine-after-bowmans-crushing-defeat/00000190-5530-dc65-abff-7d3b59640000</link><description>众议员贾马尔·鲍曼的盟友表示，他周二的失败不应被视为对美国人对加沙战争看法的公投，而他的批评者则表示，这表明对以色列持批评态度是一种选举责任。哪个更准确？</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 17:46:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/can-progressives-tackle-the-pro-israel-machine-after-bowmans-crushing-defeat/00000190-5530-dc65-abff-7d3b59640000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 264 天：联合国表示加沙援助人员面临的风险“无法忍受”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-264-un-says-risk-to-aid-workers-in-gaza-intolerable/00000190-555b-de50-af9b-7fffdece0000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，由于内塔尼亚胡政府提出的要求减少，美国对以色列的武器运输已放缓 ■ 以色列国防部长加兰特表示，即使美国和以色列存在分歧，“我们也会闭门解决” ■ 以色列监狱管理局一直在隐瞒信息消息人士称，自战争开始以来，巴勒斯坦囚犯获得的食物数量如下： 战争进入 264 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 16:28:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-264-un-says-risk-to-aid-workers-in-gaza-intolerable/00000190-555b-de50-af9b-7fffdece0000</guid></item><item><title>我的高中毕业生面临着以色列有史以来最黯淡的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-high-school-graduates-are-facing-the-bleakest-future-israel-has-ever-known/00000190-5406-dc65-abff-7c2fb42c0000</link><description>我可以诚实地向我的学生保证国家和以色列国防军会保护他们吗？或者以色列仍将是一个民主国家？不会发生内战吗？他们在这里将过着怎样的生活？</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-high-school-graduates-are-facing-the-bleakest-future-israel-has-ever-known/00000190-5406-dc65-abff-7c2fb42c0000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列减少了巴勒斯坦安全囚犯的食物，并隐瞒了数据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-reduces-food-for-palestinian-security-prisoners-conceals-data-sources-say/00000190-542e-de5e-abd0-ff7ee9580000</link><description>自10月7日起，监狱内食物大幅减少，囚犯体重减轻，甚至挨饿。当以色列最高法院听取有关此事的请愿书时，极右翼部长本格维尔表示这是一项“威慑措施”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:52:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-reduces-food-for-palestinian-security-prisoners-conceals-data-sources-say/00000190-542e-de5e-abd0-ff7ee9580000</guid></item><item><title>事实还是虚构：以色列受到全球谴责是否不公平？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/fact-or-fiction-is-israel-unfairly-singled-out-for-global-condemnation/00000190-5053-d37f-a392-7afbfbaf0000</link><description>“有偏见、预定、虚伪”：以色列的支持者这样形容国际社会在人权和国际法方面的态度。事实上，在加沙战争之前，令人震惊的是以色列所享受的长期、免费的​​旅程</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:33:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/fact-or-fiction-is-israel-unfairly-singled-out-for-global-condemnation/00000190-5053-d37f-a392-7afbfbaf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列知名人士在《纽约时报》撰文敦促国会废除内塔尼亚胡的演讲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israelis-pen-op-ed-in-new-york-times-urging-congress-to-axe-pm-speech/00000190-5471-de50-af9b-7ffdfb730000</link><description>该报告由包括前总理巴拉克和前摩萨德局长在内的六名以色列人共同撰写，皮尔斯敦促国会撤回内塔尼亚胡的邀请，“因为大部分以色列人对内塔尼亚胡先生的政府失去了信心”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:13:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israelis-pen-op-ed-in-new-york-times-urging-congress-to-axe-pm-speech/00000190-5471-de50-af9b-7ffdfb730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长赞扬法国极右党主席，打破以色列官方抵制全国集会的行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/minister-praises-frances-far-right-party-president-breaking-israels-official-boycott/00000190-53c3-d31c-afb9-dfd39a180000</link><description>侨民部长阿米凯·奇克利（Amichai Chikli）赞扬了法国极右翼全国集会主席乔丹·巴尔德拉（Jordan Bardella）发表的讲话，他在讲话中宣布两国解决方案“过时”，巴勒斯坦建国是“恐怖的奖励”。奇克利办公室：“我们与勒庞党有良好的接触”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 11:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/minister-praises-frances-far-right-party-president-breaking-israels-official-boycott/00000190-53c3-d31c-afb9-dfd39a180000</guid></item><item><title>“离开这座城市，犹太人！”：犹太儿童在伦敦涉嫌仇恨犯罪中遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/get-out-of-the-city-jew-jewish-children-assaulted-in-alleged-hate-crime-in-london/00000190-5401-de5e-abd0-ff73cf470000</link><description>一群东正教男孩在中央地铁站遭到当地另一所学校的孩子们的袭击。其中一名男孩的母亲说：“他们把他的头撞到墙上，一颗牙齿脱落了。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:43:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/get-out-of-the-city-jew-jewish-children-assaulted-in-alleged-hate-crime-in-london/00000190-5401-de5e-abd0-ff73cf470000</guid></item><item><title>“黎巴嫩的战争不会是与真主党的决斗；以色列将面临伊朗的整个抵抗轴心”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-26/ty-article-podcast/in-a-war-with-hezbollah-israel-will-face-irans-entire-axis-of-resistance/00000190-53a1-de5e-abd0-fbf3be140000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-26/ty-article-podcast/in-a-war-with-hezbollah-israel-will-face-irans-entire-axis-of-resistance/00000190-53a1-de5e-abd0-fbf3be140000</guid></item><item><title>摇摇欲坠的内塔尼亚胡联盟改变了正统派的现状——变得更糟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/haredim-in-no-hurry-to-exit-govt-but-top-court-ruling-widens-cracks-in-the-coalition/00000190-53c0-ddd9-a1f1-d3f286b30000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡对最高法院对草案裁决的回应具有误导性和煽动性。一些人预计他会继续宣传甘茨的“豁免法”，只是为了争取时间，因为他知道法院会否决它</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/haredim-in-no-hurry-to-exit-govt-but-top-court-ruling-widens-cracks-in-the-coalition/00000190-53c0-ddd9-a1f1-d3f286b30000</guid></item></channel></rss>